64
00:05:19,528 --> 00:05:20,529
[Woo-seok] <i>Suriah?</i>

65
00:05:22,614 --> 00:05:23,615
[menghela napas]

66
00:05:34,084 --> 00:05:36,420
Anda bisa saja berakhir seperti itu.

67
00:05:37,296 --> 00:05:38,464
Sudah kubilang

68
00:05:38,964 --> 00:05:40,799
